    "These data are encoded into structured prompts that convey a comprehensive environmental context to the LLM.",
    "This encoding ensures that the LLM receives timely, accurate input representing dynamic changes in the environment. 2.",
    "Python extension integration: NetLogo uses its Python extension to facilitate communication with GPT-4o via the OpenAI API.",
    "This extension allows NetLogo to send encoded environmental data as prompts to the LLM and receive structured responses, enabling the interaction between the simulation platform and the LLM. 3.",
    "LLM processing: The structured prompts are processed by GPT-4o, which interprets the input data and generates agent behavior suggestions based on encoded environmental information."
